text: Lisa Unruh is an archer from Germany. She was born on 12 April 1988. Unruh competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Lisa UnruhLisa UNRUH == References == Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:German archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for Germany Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Germany
